Method Detail

getOnlineStatus

public void getOnlineStatus(SwarmUser.GotUserStatusCB cb)
Get the SwarmUser's online status and if the user is online, which SwarmApplication the user is logged into.

Parameters:
cb - When successful, the GotUserStatusCB callback returns a boolean that indicates if this SwarmUser is online (true) or offline (false). The GotUserStatusCB callback also returns the SwarmApplication app object to indicate which Swarm-enabled application the user is currently logged in to. If the user is not online the SwarmApplication app object is null.
